/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 940, \"end\": 944, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9995841300807765, \"rank\": 0.00027614435350648643, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 974, \"end\": 980, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"score\": 0.999996656987736, \"rank\": 2.825048297694391e-06, \"text\": \"Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The sport\", \"from\": 830, \"to\": 839}, {\"ngram\": \"breaking madeits\", \"from\": 843, \"to\": 859}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic debut\", \"from\": 860, \"to\": 873}, {\"ngram\": \"its most viral images\", \"from\": 895, \"to\": 916}, {\"ngram\": \"the performance\", \"from\": 921, \"to\": 936}, {\"ngram\": \"a university professor\", \"from\": 946, \"to\": 968}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"kangaroo dance\", \"from\": 991, \"to\": 1008}, {\"ngram\": \"other moves\", \"from\": 1016, \"to\": 1027}, {\"ngram\": \"her routine\", \"from\": 1035, \"to\": 1046}, {\"ngram\": \"a single point\", \"from\": 1069, \"to\": 1083}, {\"ngram\": \"the nine judges\", \"from\": 1096, \"to\": 1111}, {\"ngram\": \"either round\", \"from\": 1115, \"to\": 1127}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gunn was subsequently mocked for her efforts, including a parody on \\\"The Tonight Show Starring Jimmy Fallon\\\" in the United States.\", \"from\": 1130, \"to\": 1260, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1130, \"end\": 1134, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9995841300807765, \"rank\": 0.00027614435350648643, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 1246, \"end\": 1259, \"title\": \"ht